        "timestamp": "2018-07-31 18:43:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nNo compiles are being generated for this code, because it is not tied in to the parent poms.\nWhen you do tie it in, you are going to have problems because you are missing key sections - like distributionManagement.  Normally, these would be inherited from the corresponding parent POM in ccsdk/parent, but instead you are directly using another project's parent - which does not give you the flexibility to inherit ONAP project settings.   You should instead create your own ccsdk parent (by copying an existing one and changing its parent to the spring boot parent you're currently using).",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
